data.description: This delightful Pool home with RV Parking, no HOA, and low tax rate. 3-bedroom, 1-bath home offers a serene and comfortable living experience with the added luxury of a private pool and solar.    Nestled on a peaceful, tree-lined street of the Valle Vista area, this residence provides the perfect blend of cozy living spaces and outdoor entertainment. As you approach the home, you'll immediately notice its curb appeal with a manicured front yard and a welcoming entryway. Wide driveway with plenty of RV / Toy space.     Inside you'll find a light-filled living area, complete with windows that bathe the room in natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, making it an ideal space for family gatherings and entertaining guests.    Three comfortable bedrooms provide plenty of room for rest and relaxation. The shared bathroom is efficiently designed, featuring a bathtub and shower combination.    Step out onto the covered patio, where you can enjoy al fresco dining and take in the view of your sparkling pool. The pool area is perfect for cooling off on hot summer days, sunbathing, or hosting poolside gatherings with friends and family. A low-maintenance, landscaped yard surrounds the pool, ensuring your outdoor space remains inviting and enjoyable year-round.    Enjoy easy access to shopping, schools, parks, and essential amenities. This home provides a perfect opportunity for anyone seeking a single-level retreat with a pool and space for RV, Campers, Toys, in a serene Southern California neighborhood.
